gcc_update: (files_and_dependencies) Add gcc/java/parse.c gcc/java/parse-scan.c and...

	* gcc_update: (files_and_dependencies) Add gcc/java/parse.c
	gcc/java/parse-scan.c and gcc/java/keyword.h to list of files to
	touch.

From-SVN: r45410
